'''''Le guceceka de la forêt''''' ni filime yerekana ikinamico yo muri Central Afurika  na Kameruni yo muri 2003 iyobowe na Bassek Ba Kobhio na Didier Ouenangare . Ni amateka ni filime ya mbere yerekanwe muri Sinema yo muri Repubulika ya Centrafrique <ref name=":0">https://www.cinemaescapist.com/2019/02/best-african-movies-list/</ref> Iyi filime kandi yakorewe hamwe muri [[Gabon]] na [[Kameruni]] . <ref>JC Woodfrok (2006) ''Culture and Customs of the Central African Republic'', Greenwood Press, pg. 150</ref> <ref>https://books.google.com/books?id=n1RiCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA224</ref> <ref>https://books.google.com/books?id=Em8kDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT72</ref> Filime yahinduwe ishingiye ku gitabo cyanditswe na [[Étienne Goyémidé]] gifite umutwe umwe ''Le guceceka de la forêt'' . <ref>http://newsreel.org/video/LE-SILENCE-DE-LA-FORET</ref> Iyi filime yari ishingiye ku moko mato ya Pygmies nyafurika kandi ni nayo filime ya mbere ivuga ku ivangura rishingiye ku ivanguramoko ry’Abanyafurika bigezweho ku bwoko bw’abasangwabutaka bo muri Afurika (Biaka people). <ref>https://www.kanopy.com/product/silence-forest</ref>

== Icegeranyo ==
Gonaba (Eriq Ebouaney), umugenzuzi w’uburezi mu karere muri Repubulika ya Centrafrique yumva acitse intege kandi acitse intege nyuma yo gukora mu butegetsi bwa gisirikare imyaka irenga icumi. Bidatinze, ashishikajwe no kunganira ubwoko bw’abasangwabutaka bwitwa Baaka muri rusange birengagizwa kandi bagafatwa nabi muri sosiyete kandi ubuzima bwabo bukaba bubangamiwe n’imijyi n’iterambere ry’ubukungu. <ref>https://www.screendaily.com/the-silence-of-the-forest-le-silence-de-la-foret/4014179.article</ref>

== Abakinnyi ==

* Eriq Ebouaney nka Gonaba
* Nadège Beausson-Diagne nka Simone
* Sonia Zembourou nka Kali
* Philippe Mory nka Perefe

Iyi filime yabanje gutangazwa ko izayoborwa gusa n’umukinnyi wa filime ukomoka muri Repubulika ya Centrafrique Didier Ouenangare nkumushinga we wa mbere. Yatangiye kuyobora bwa mbere binyuze muri uyu mushinga afite imyaka 50.  Icyakora umuyobozi wa Kameruni Bassek Ba Kobhio yinjiye mu gufata amashusho kandi ashinzwe ibijyanye na tekiniki yo kurasa. Bassek yaje kuba umuyobozi mukuru wa film mugihe Didier yamubereye umuyobozi wa film. Bombi bumvikanye gukorana kandi film yatewe inkunga cyane na Kameruni na Gabon. Iyi filime yakorewe muri CAR mu gihe igihugu cyahuye n’ibibazo by’ubukungu hamwe n’ubutegetsi bwa gisirikare mu 2003 . Byagaragaye ko umukinnyi wa firime Didier yakiriye inkunga ingana na 50000 FF na Agence intergouvernmentale de la francophonie mugihe cy'ibirori bya Amiens. <ref name=":1">http://africultures.com/co-director-of-le-silence-de-la-foret-5698/</ref>

Benshi mubagize itsinda hamwe nabatekinisiye mugikorwa cyo gufata amashusho bashakishijwe mubihugu duturanye birimo Kameruni na Gabon. Umukinnyi wa filime wo muri Kameruni, Eriq Ebouaney yatoranijwe kugira ngo agire uruhare runini kandi yagombaga kwiga ururimi rwa Sango rukaba ari rumwe mu ndimi zemewe za Repubulika ya Centrafrique. Umuhimbyi w’umuziki wamamaye muri Kameruni, Manu Dibango, yinjijwe mu muziki wa filime. Umuyobozi wa firime Didier nawe yakiriye opposition no kunengwa kuba adahisemo abanyafurika yo hagati ngo bakore iyo film. 

== Kurekura ==
Iyi filime yerekanwe mu gihugu muri Repubulika ya Centrafrique yarahungabanye kubera ko sinema yonyine mu gihugu yari ifunze icyo gihe.  Filime yatoranijwe kumugaragaro kugirango yerekanwe mu minsi mikuru mike ya firime kandi ifunguye muri rusange ibitekerezo byiza byatanzwe nabanegura. Iyi filime yerekanwe ku gice cy’umubumbe wa Afurika mu2003 Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Toronto 2003. <ref>https://www.digitalhit.com/torontofilmfestival/2003/filmlist</ref> Yatoranijwe kandi kugirango yerekanwe mu gice cy’abayobozi ba Fortnight igice cya Festival ya Cannes 2003 . <ref>http://www.quinzaine-realisateurs.com/qz_an/2003/</ref> Iyi filime kandi yakiriwe cyane mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime 2003 ryitwa Francophone de Namur (FIFF). <ref>http://africultures.com/namur-2003-la-resistance-francophone-3068/</ref>

